Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.36,0:00:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.64,0:00:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.16,0:00:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.46,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.84,0:00:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.50,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.76,0:01:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.57,0:01:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第48话 想回到相遇的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是防止化脓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是止痛的涂抹药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.60,0:02:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  纱布与绷带我带了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那么我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要回去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是送药过来而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  至少和犬夜叉握手言和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再为了小事就吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.65,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和犬夜叉吵过架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从奈落手里保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我而已不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架的事我居然完全忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇无精打采的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.26,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…这也不是没有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个光是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.01,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  戈薇姑娘又回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.89,0:04:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你和桔梗见面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且让戈薇姑娘看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…被看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还厚着脸皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你满面佛光喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.91,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  那种大彻大悟的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉似乎打算说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为我害怕听见而逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.28,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉一定下定决心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因奈落的陷阱而彼此憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗亦追随犬夜叉而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且拆散两人的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度袭击桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保护你的只有我而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.38,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有我介入的余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是放不下桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  我已经不会再见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能再见你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗为了犬夜叉\N连命都豁出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本比不上她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也无法回到犬夜叉那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉也不会来接我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.12,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把四魂碎片带来这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是还给他比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…把这个还回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一切都会结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我则回到普通的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就回来不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从回来之后又都不说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大拇指?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和犬夜叉哥哥吵架了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈…\N爸爸  方便的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这份荷包蛋给你吃好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些腌罗卜很有口感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道很不错喔  吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  碗不用洗没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会我会一起洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈…\N姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道妈妈都不担心姐姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个腌罗卜真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出院了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.22,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是身体\N出现了不明的斑点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装病的理由跟点子用光了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且不管这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后如何了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再装傻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是和先前明明脚踏两条船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爱吃醋的\N粗暴任性男人的关系呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实的分手了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像说了什么不该说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎狠狠的被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是戈薇甩掉他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还喜欢着那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  已经完全没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不在意了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以就什么都别再问了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再碰触伤口的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种假笑好恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇跟钢牙要好一点就发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却一心一意的跟桔梗跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了这么轻率的理由吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  去见戈薇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定再也不去见她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有搞错啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要你取回被戈薇姑娘\N带回去的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能通过那口井吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了四魂碎片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是戈薇怎么样无所谓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉已经选择了桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戈薇姑娘回来才是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉啊  这样真的妥当吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦  枫姥姥连你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由骨灰与土所创造的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.55,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是不属于\N这个世界的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  魂魄还是桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.99,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底\N你们在这世上是无法结合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.36,0:11:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗姐姐想要的\N只是和你共赴黄泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓  就如桔梗所愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她一同下地狱去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是我与桔梗的命运…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片得拿去还他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.53,0:12:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…我好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果归还这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也见不到犬夜叉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟随桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.67,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有桔梗的话就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是这么坏的女人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的表情一定很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的表情不能和犬夜叉相见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…这棵树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.97,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是  将犬夜叉封印的树吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.11,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里  第一次遇见犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么呆滞的表情啊  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经老的痴呆了吗  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一箭解决它啊  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像上次解决我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗桔梗的  到底在叫谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好了\N我的名字叫做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要和他相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如当初不要相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再一次见到犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.68,0:14:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然喜欢上犬夜叉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.69,0:14:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时  变得这么喜欢他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.87,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你待在神木的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感受到什么\N不可思议的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛自己变的更诚实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得自己的心思\N也愈来愈清晰吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年接受你爸爸求婚的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈当然很喜欢你爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是求婚前几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却为了一点琐事吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于能不能顺利的往下发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一走到这棵树下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也变的更加诚实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就OK了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.13,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏如此  得到了戈薇与草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈很感谢这棵树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不会过问戈薇在烦恼什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈相信戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为戈薇是会朝自己\N深信的道路勇往直前的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.75,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去见戈薇对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道为什么不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.64,0:16:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那就等于向戈薇道别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候没能说出口的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要传达给她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在最痛苦的人不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是戈薇姑娘才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.86,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉是已经下定决心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.43,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想戈薇现在一定非常苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去找戈薇把话说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的做个了结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  什么事都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.17,0:17:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…巴不得我和戈薇分开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想分开吗\N你不想分开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.71,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…谁会在意这种小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定要保护桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我怎能再说出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到戈薇身边这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.89,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不到黄河心不死的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就叫他劈腿男吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还比他振作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能说“回来吧”这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇应该很清楚才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有好好的见个面道别的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里也放不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.48,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对面的这期间  我一直在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  桔梗还有我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  其实我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为了解犬夜叉的心情  所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我已经不能再待在这了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遇到你之前  谁都不信任我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你会为了我而掉泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和戈薇在一起我很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.98,0:19:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我无法时而高兴时而欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗追随着我而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我必须舍命报答桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我比不上桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也考虑了许多桔梗的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗与我是完全不一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.01,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使说我是桔梗的转世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我毕竟不是桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心是我自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N我只能理解一种桔梗的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能再见犬夜叉一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到桔梗\N也和我有相同的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得轻松点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然想要相见的心情是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才鼓起勇气来见犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也很想见你一面  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和犬夜叉在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我无法忘记你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇…我该怎么回答才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你在一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.09,0:21:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要…和我在一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉与桔梗的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能斩断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.64,0:21:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犬夜叉  我是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.85,0:21:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你相遇绝对不是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望犬夜叉能继续活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你充满欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.95,0:22:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道能为你做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想一直待在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.47,0:22:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.74,0:22:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.99,0:22:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.80,0:23:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.45,0:23:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.79,0:23:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.29,0:23:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.73,0:23:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.49,0:23:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠亲切的老爷爷\N与老婆婆的琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪竟然追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.69,0:23:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是夺取背上的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.50,0:23:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然遇上的我们
